summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of East John Street, from Thirty-sixth Avenue North to Thirty seventh Avenue North, et al, in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete walks under Ordinance No. 19025, creating Local Improvement District No. 1833 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
